Focus-mode Robfly program:

While browsing websites, we encounter visuals that prevent us from focusing attention. This is an application that makes images invisible. In this way, reading and watching videos will be more enjoyable instead of unnecessary banners.

This software hides unnecessary banners. This makes it easier for us to focus only on our area of ​​interest.

Robfly Software team.
